We have recommended that the Management:

Require the Sangguniang Bayan to enact a resolution prescribing the policies and guidelines on the grant of donations/financial assistance containing the following:

Kind of financial assistance (medical, educational, funeral, etc.;

Approval limits for specific cases, including the frequency of grants to each individual;

Criteria in the granting of donation and the documentary requirements for each particular assistance;

All cases must be referred to the MSWDO for eligibility evaluation and the case study report prepared must be made part of the supporting documents of the claim.

Require the Municipal Accountant to ensure that all payments are adequately and properly supported with the required documents to support the validity and regularity of claims; and

Refrain from charging SEF related activities against Donations as this practice depletes the budget for intended activities.

